Nissan Motor Corp U.S.A. saiddomestic car sales in the February 21 to 28 period rose to3,501 from 2,578 cars at the same time last year.    For the month of February, U.S. car sales increased to7,200 from 6,843 cars in the comparable month a year ago,Nissan Motor, a wholly-owned subsidiary of Nissan Motor Ltdsaid .    For the year-to-date, Nissan Motor domestic sales advancedto 13,769 cars from 12,846 cars in 1986, the automaker said. Reuter&#3;